entry.name: The Pan-Human Library: A repository of assays to quantify 10 000 proteins by SWATH-MS
entry.description: The “Pan-Human Library” is a compendium of highly specific assays covering more than 10 000 human proteins and enabling their targeted analysis in SWATH-MS datasets acquired from research or clinical specimens.

additional_fields.field: Cell culture and Tissue sampling, Protein fractionation (AP, SEC, Depletion, None), Proteolytic digestion (Trypsin, PCT), Peptide fractionation (OGE, 1D GE, SAX, None), LC-MS/MS
Shotgun database search (X!Tandem, MyriMatch, OMSSA, Comet), Statistical evaluation (PeptideProphet, iProphet), FDR control (MAYU)
No PTMs are included in the dataset
